01:31.743 --> 01:32.440
You're going to
be late for school.

01:32.614 --> 01:34.268
Jesus H. Christ.

01:34.442 --> 01:36.052
[Alex] Especially
when reminded that

01:36.226 --> 01:39.186
his 16 year old daughter
actually looks 16.

01:39.360 --> 01:41.057
[Carey] Does no one
wear clothes anymore?

01:41.231 --> 01:42.928
[sighs]

01:43.103 --> 01:46.497
[Alex] My mother,
meanwhile, enjoys smiling.

01:46.671 --> 01:49.718
She works in PR,
which is by its very nature,

01:49.892 --> 01:52.286
the most superficial
of superficial professions.

01:53.330 --> 01:54.984
Still,

01:55.158 --> 01:56.768
-it plays to her strength.
-Good to see you.

01:56.942 --> 01:59.075
