there's a direct correlation

02:04.559 --> 02:06.126
between said detachment

02:06.300 --> 02:07.431
and dead eyed
Cheshire cat grinning.

02:09.912 --> 02:12.436
Privately, that detachment
takes a different form.

02:12.958 --> 02:14.830
[Judith] Yeah, Carey and I
are taking the girls

02:15.004 --> 02:16.266
